"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641278686,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"Kc0arcyyt6xGt0n2GoedRwS7k0EJ2143oYAdY3m_t08\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x86C65F623b7A121ffE63627249800226f49C75fB\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rx4021zRrgVaaaA3sl7C1TEtrPL3dc1uvyNYUTHRkUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yUKZS87LACQmzpnnfbR_9H5IKYTlraf5Q9CE73tkIec\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"id072wsLpyUWEFvAzXKDPpV19LjZDi7oTxjcz6drouj6uoEMDDeOMNOUQhLtRPbUfnRXjXD9IoN1n2yNDF5SAw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x98481718e5cee14235b3f2d20a7b675811be78970e3a657d98056bcdae99de71266f424a3c3480ed9cd1d114ff9230b545f091c3ed047c9d3b8314b05a003c521c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"rx4021zRrgVaaaA3sl7C1TEtrPL3dc1uvyNYUTHRkUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"yUKZS87LACQmzpnnfbR_9H5IKYTlraf5Q9CE73tkIec\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi